"structures anterior abdomen and perinium, external approach. this class includes one or more of 18 standard surgical interventions or procedures on component parts of the structures of the anterior abdomen and perinium with external approach.  these surgical interventions or procedures are listed in the world health organizations international statistical classification of diseases and related health problems or icd-10 pcs under code 0w.. . "
"structures anterior abdomen and perinium, external approach. this class includes one or more of 18 standard surgical interventions or procedures on component parts of the structures of the anterior abdomen and perinium with external approach.  these surgical interventions or procedures are listed in the world health organizations international statistical classification of diseases and related health problems or icd-10 pcs under code 0w.. revision of other device in female perineum,  external approach. this classification denotes the group of activities that yields a surgical intervention or procedure to revision of other device in female perineum,  external approach.this surgical intervention or procedure is listed in the world health organizations international statistical classification of diseases and related health problems or icd-10 as code 0wwnxyz. "

"

"

"

"
